.TH MODELLING_CELLGRAPH 1 2026-4月 "" "Run the cell graph structure modelling workflow"
.SH NAME
modelling_cellgraph \- modelling_cellgraph(src,
    <i>outputdir</i> = <span style='color: blue !important;'>NULL</span>,
    <i>up.len</i> = <span style='color: green;'>150</span>,
    <i>localdb</i> = <span style='color: blue !important;'>NULL</span>,
    <i>diamond</i> = 'Sys.which'('diamond'),
    <i>n.threads</i> = <span style='color: green;'>32</span>)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fImodelling_cellgraph(src,
    <i>outputdir</i> = <span style='color: blue !important;'>NULL</span>,
    <i>up.len</i> = <span style='color: green;'>150</span>,
    <i>localdb</i> = <span style='color: blue !important;'>NULL</span>,
    <i>diamond</i> = 'Sys.which'('diamond'),
    <i>n.threads</i> = <span style='color: green;'>32</span>)\fR
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\fBsrc\fB \fR\- . the ncbi genbank assembly source file its file path
.PP
.PP
\fBoutputdir\fB \fR\- NULL. the result outputdir and temp workspace
location, default value is NULL means use the parent dir of
the input src
.PP
.PP
\fBup.len\fB \fR\- 150. 
.PP
.PP
\fBlocaldb\fB \fR\- NULL. 
.PP
.PP
\fBdiamond\fB \fR\- 'Sys.which'('diamond'). 
.PP
.PP
\fBn.threads\fB \fR\- 32. 
.PP
.SH VALUE
.PP
this function has no return value, and then generated virtual
cell model file will be saved at the ``outputdir`` with a fixed
file name: ``model.vcell``. and the output dir also contains a html/pdf
report about the virtual cell modelling result.
.PP
.SH FILES
.PP
SMRUCC/R#.declare_function.modelling_cellgraph at main.R:line 15
.PP
